        sourceData.evaluation.fullLabelCompatibility
        (part.toThetaCuspClassContainerAudit.theta_source.compatible_average.cuspLogVolume
          audited) ∧
      part.toThetaCuspClassContainerAudit.theta_source.compatible_average.cuspLogVolume
